        "## Section 4 — Apply LoRA Adapters (PEFT)\n",
        "Instead of updating all 8B parameters, LoRA injects small trainable matrices\n",
        "into the attention layers. Only ~0.1% of parameters are trained — this is why\n",
        "fine-tuning fits on a 16GB T4."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
